snippet.title: Cybrix Trailer - Now on App Lab
snippet.description:
The Sportif Arcade Style Workout Application. Your goal is to destroy every single brick by swinging the rackets, shooting with laser guns and detonating the explosive ball all while dodging shrapnel, mines, charging up the piercing ball and collecting power-ups. Compete against your friends on the global leaderboard in 50 different levels or try to get as far as you can in the endless mode.

Cybrix on App Lab:
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4625005897550253

DISCORD: https://discord.gg/rRsQEew
WEBSITE: https://www.holonautic.com/cybrix

To follow up on updates and future announcements you can also follow us on Twitter:
